  "title": "37 Nearer, My God To Thee",
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "type": "verse",
      "lines": [
        "Nearer,my God,to Thee,",
        "Nearer to thee!",
        "E’en tho’ it be a cross",
        "That raiseth me!",
        "Still all my song shall be,",
        "Nearer my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer to Thee."
      ],
      "number": 1
    },
    {
      "type": "verse",
      "lines": [
        "Tho’ like a wonderer, Day-light all gone,",
        "Darkness be over me,",
        "My rest a stone;",
        "Yet in my dreams I’d be",
        "Nearer my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer, my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer to Thee."
      ],
      "number": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "verse",
      "lines": [
        "There let the way appear, Steps up to heav’n,",
        "All that thou sendest me",
        "In mercy giv’n; Angels to beckon me,",
        "Nearer my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer to Thee."
      ],
      "number": 3
    },
    {
      "type": "verse",
      "lines": [
        "Then, with my watching tho’ts Bright with thy praise,",
        "Out of my stormy griefs, Bethel I’ll raise;",
        "So by my woes to be,",
        "Nearer, my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer, my God to Thee,",
        "Nearer to Thee."
      ],
      "number": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "verse",
      "lines": [
        "Or, if on joyful wing Cleaving the sky,",
        "Sun, moon, and stars forgot",
        "Upward I fly, Still all my song shall be,",
        "Nearer, my God, to Thee,",
        "Nearer, my God, to Thee,",
        "Nearer to Thee."
      ],
      "number": 5
    }
  ]
